description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 2 Critical Care Technician to join our Critical Care team at East Sussex Healthcare NHS Trust, Conquest Hospital. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Critical Care is a 14 bedded unit, which has level 2 and level 3 dependent patients.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking to recruit a highly motivated and enthusiastic individual to work within our well-established team of nurses and healthcare assistants to provide excellent support to our patients and their families, as well as contribute to the smooth running of our Critical Care Unit. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will have excellent communication skills, be able to work well in a team and be able to work flexibly according to the day-to-day needs of the unit. Ideally you will have experience in a hospital care setting. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This post is full time ( job share would be considered) working predominantly 11.5 hour shifts, internal rotation, both during the week and weekend.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Informal visits to the unit encouraged. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameCaroline EllisJob titleMatron Critical CareEmail addresscaroline.ellis5@nhs.netTelephone number03001314500 ext 735117 / 734526&lt;/p&gt;
